		<p>I'm sharing the <a href="http://senate.universityofcalifornia.edu/_files/reports/JC-JN-Assembly-Budget-Bill.pdf">system-wide Academic Council's concerns</a> about the State Assembly Budget bill that proposes direct allocation of state funds to UCOP and withholds funding from the University. Also, i expect to post the summaries of the <i>2016/2017 Cluster Hiring Survey</i> and the <i>Survey of 2013-2016 UCR Faculty Hires</i> in the coming weeks.</p>
		<p>Have a safe summer.</p>
		<p>dylan</p>
	</fieldset>
